ally an iPad Pro with a less fancy screen that starts at $599 instead of $799.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-ipad-pro-2022-m2-review-140026198-140026510-140026377-140026181.html"><strong>Read our full review of the Apple iPad Pro</strong></a></p><h2> Best Android tablet: Samsung Galaxy Tab S8</h2><p><core-commerce id="dc610303f4f04eaf9c9f165f9f36fd19" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Available in three sizes – an 11-, 12.4- and a huge 14.6-inch model – <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmODVlNjNjZC1lMTNjLTRmOWQtOTkxYy05ZmJhYWRlZGUzYWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vL3VzL3RhYmxldHMvZ2FsYXh5LXRhYi1zOC9idXkvPyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjcxOTRhN2QtODQzNS00ODAyLThlYzAtM2JmZGI3ZDk5Y2JhIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZCniMx19ogWMeFLnLcE1sY069Ff6Up7nANYmmyR8Yac&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2F%2Fus%2Ftablets%2Fgalaxy-tab-s8%2Fbuy%2F%3F">Samsung&#39;s Galaxy Tab S8 line</a> has the right-sized screen for practically any need. And while Android typically isn&#39;t quite as accommodating to productivity as Windows or iPadOS, Samsung&#39;s Dex mode offers a desktop-like UI complete with multi-window support and a taskbar for potent multitasking.</p><p> Samsung&#39;s tablet displays are also some of the best in the business, with support for 120Hz refresh rates and vibrant colors from their OLED panels. And unlike Samsung&#39;s flagship phone line, the <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s-8-review-in-a-class-of-its-own-132946024.html">Galaxy Tab S8</a> still comes with microSD card support, though sadly, Samsung couldn&#39;t seem to find room for a dedicated headphone jack. The tablet comes with an S pen stylus as well, and you get a choice of three different covers: a <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmODVlNjNjZC1lMTNjLTRmOWQtOTkxYy05ZmJhYWRlZGUzYWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vL3VzL21vYmlsZS9tb2JpbGUtYWNjZXNzb3JpZXMvdGFibGV0cy9nYWxheHktdGFiLXM4LWJvb2stY292ZXIta2V5Ym9hcmQtc2xpbS1lZi1kdDYzMHViZWd1ai8_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyNzE5NGE3ZC04NDM1LTQ4MDItOGVjMC0zYmZkYjdkOTljYmEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAARbvCUYx3PzCPtpKHDqupPAsW01K_aqFAIrQ59XKR_L8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2F%2Fus%2Fmobile%2Fmobile-accessories%2Ftablets%2Fgalaxy-tab-s8-book-cover-keyboard-slim-ef-dt630ubeguj%2F%3F">simple folio</a> , a <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASU8I4w_xsqUTWYVxj87QWQxIJ6V3a0qy7iq7wElYdBu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2F%2Fus%2Fmobile%2Fmobile-accessories%2Ftablets%2Fgalaxy-tab-s8-plus-galaxy-tab-s7-fe-book-cover-keyboard-slim-black-ef-dt730ubeguj%2F%3F">keyboard cover</a> and a <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeg3ZisCRRlbt6I3VF0gqteJABvzC7R7fSk8jGlaBPy7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2F%2Fus%2Fmobile%2Fmobile-accessories%2Ftablets%2Fgalaxy-t